<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw, Lalpa, chungnung pen, ka hun chawian ui,
 Pathien Hing leh Bang cheng bawlthei chuh na hi;
 Nuoisiehte suok, liengvai, migilote Guol,
 Chagahte, gimtheite (3) Lal, Pa leh Pathien.

[V2]
 2. Pauchamna dawngpa Pathien na hih ziekin,
 Na miten taksap a ngetnau Na pie zing;
 Na chate kap leh tauna Na ngaitha zing,
 Thudik zui, thilpha bawl, (3) Na nungsawn ngei puoi.

[V3]
 3. Chun, ziehi milien leh mineu hetsak in,
 Mipite leh Nangmah ngei hun do pen ten;
 &quot;Tuhin hukdama ka um theihna dingun,
 Banga ka bawl ding uh (3) tiu hen la Amen.

[V4]
 4. Namtin thim leh suok pawtsan kipak u hen,
 &quot;Chungnung pena Pathien lopi pen hen la;
 Lei chunga A lawpte chungah cham leng hen,
 Hossana! Hossana! (3) ti'n la hun sau hen.

[V5]
 5. Chun micheng kiengah na min hung zahum hen;
 Na gam lopi takin hung tung zel hen la;
 Van miten a bawl bangun leia mite'n,
 Na deihguol bawl u hen, (3) gam tin ah, Amen.</lyrics>
<title>WE PRAISE THEE, O LORD</title>
<hymn_number>332</hymn_number>
</song>